Module lanej.inventorysystem

Package lanej.inventorysystem.model

package lanej.inventorysystem.model
This package primarily provides the classes used to abstract the handling of inventory items within the inventory management software.

The `Inventory` class serves as the main point of access for managing the inventory data and provides methods for adding, deleting, and updating products and parts.

The `Part` and `Product` classes provide model objects for representing inventory items and have methods for getting and setting properties.

The `InHouse` and `Outsourced` classes extend the `Part` class to provide more specific types of parts, with additional properties and methods.
